content.description: this job will read data from Metal stage and load to bronze scd2 tables.
content.name: cdi_tsk_adm_t_agency_bronze_load_rank

transformations.description: this source to capture the daily data from metal table
transformations.name: src_t_agency

object.customQuery:
WITH current_batch AS (
    SELECT 
        bls.batch_id,
        bls.source_start_cutoff_datetime,
        bls.source_end_cutoff_datetime
    FROM metal.batch_load_summary bls
    WHERE bls.source_system_code = 'Guidewire'
      AND bls.batch_status = 'Inprogress'
      AND bls.batch_id = (
          SELECT MAX(batch_id)
          FROM metal.batch_load_summary
          WHERE source_system_code = 'Guidewire'
            AND batch_status = 'Inprogress'
      )
)

SELECT DISTINCT
    metal_agency.source_name,
    metal_agency.load_type,
    metal_agency.agency_nup,
    metal_agency.agency_num,
    metal_agency.location_num,
    metal_agency.location_type,
    metal_agency.agency_is_super,
    metal_agency.agency_is_enabled,
    metal_agency.agency_name,
    metal_agency.agency_second_name,
    metal_agency.agency_str_1,
    metal_agency.agency_str_2,
    metal_agency.agency_str_3,
    metal_agency.agency_city,
    metal_agency.agency_st,
    metal_agency.agency_zip,
    metal_agency.agency_contact_firstname,
    metal_agency.agency_contact_lastname,
    metal_agency.agency_contact_phone,
    metal_agency.agency_contact_fax,
    metal_agency.agency_contact_email_address,
    metal_agency.agency_claims_email_address,
    metal_agency.agency_website_address,
    metal_agency.agency_is_grouped,
    metal_agency.agency_connection_type,
    metal_agency.agency_alternative_phone,
    metal_agency.agency_agent_type,
    metal_agency.agency_adjustment_period,
    metal_agency.agency_combine_producer_code,
    metal_agency.agency_branch,
    metal_agency.agency_fieldman,
    metal_agency.default_choicepoint_acct,
    metal_agency.gw_choicepoint_acct,
    metal_agency.agency_locator_on,
    metal_agency.is_boa_enabled,
    metal_agency.fid_num,
    metal_agency.fid_type,
    metal_agency.lexis_ivans_y_number,
    metal_agency.user_who_modified,
    metal_agency.last_modified,
    metal_agency.create_date,
    bronze_agency.t_agency_row_id ,
    current_batch.batch_id,
    current_batch.source_start_cutoff_datetime,
    current_batch.source_end_cutoff_datetime
FROM metal.adm_t_agency metal_agency
LEFT JOIN bronze.adm_t_agency bronze_agency 
    ON metal_agency.agency_nup = bronze_agency.agency_id
   AND metal_agency.agency_num = bronze_agency.agency_number
   AND metal_agency.user_who_modified = bronze_agency.last_user_who_modified
   AND metal_agency.create_date = bronze_agency.t_agency_date_created
   AND metal_agency.last_modified = bronze_agency.t_agency_date_modified
CROSS JOIN current_batch
WHERE  bronze_agency.t_agency_row_id IS NULL
  --AND metal_agency.create_date BETWEEN current_batch.source_start_cutoff_datetime  AND current_batch.source_end_cutoff_datetime
ORDER BY 
    metal_agency.agency_nup,
    metal_agency.agency_num,
    metal_agency.create_date,
    metal_agency.last_modified
